owed that actual paragraphs were always >90% alphanumeric, while strings from images of Google Maps, phone backgrounds, and my snapchats (all gibberish) varied around 55%. I decided to reject anything below 75%."), mdx("p", null, "At this point I was finally done my first Android app!"), mdx("h3", {
